\b\i\fs24 * Description *      \par
\b0\i0\fs20\par
The second mission of my six-mission campaign. In this mission, finally you enter the heart of Rocksbourg. \par
Unfortunately, things don't go as you expected...\par
\par
This mission is the sequel to \'ab\~A New Beginning\~\'bb. To understand the whole story, you should \par
play that mission before starting \'ab\~Discovery\~\'bb.\par
\par
Because this is my second mission, and I knew better the possibilities of DromEd, this is more balanced \par
than the first. But due to the high number of cells, there still might be some bugs.\par
\par
Enjoy!\par
\par
